cross: Cymbidium Lambert Day x Cymbidium Karen Hawaiian

measurements.description: Sixty-eight flowers on three 70-cm arching inflorescences; sepals yellow overlaid light red, stronger apically; petals yellow overlaid light red, stronger medially; lip bright yellow blotched red, darker orange-red bar distally on midlobe; column yellow overlaid red, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
